Usage: MDHOP [-F] [-A] [#channel]
  Mass dehalfops channel

  If passed -F friends with the H flag set will not be dehalfopped.
  -A will dehalfop all users.

See also:
  MHOP
  MOP
  MREOP
  MDOP
  MASSV
